        <trans-unit id="103" translate="yes" xml:space="preserve">
          <source>When you are using a <ph id="ph1">&lt;xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.PowerPacks.DataRepeater&gt;</ph> control that contains many records, you may want to let users search for a specific record.</source>
